List of components
------------------

- Raspberry Pi Zero W
- SD Card (>= 128 GB)
- BMP180: air pressure and temperature sensor (i2c)
- PCF8591: a/d converter (i2c) for monitoring battery status
- SSD1306: display (i2c)
- ULN2803: darlington transistor array, used as status LED driver

- Camera
  Raspberry Pi V2.1, 8 MP 1080P
- Push buttons (for switching camera on/off)
- Adafruit Ultimate GPS Breakout - 66 channel w/10 Hz updates - Version 3
  https://learn.adafruit.com/adafruit-ultimate-gps-on-the-raspberry-pi/setting-everything-up
- USB to TTL converter
  https://de.aliexpress.com/item/CJMCU-CP2102-MICRO-USB-to-UART-TTL-Module-6Pin-Serial-Converter-UART-STC-Replace-FT232-NEW/32587986095.html
- Active GPS antenna with uFL connector (if SMA, an adapter uFL - SMA is needed)
- Battery box for six AA akkus
- M8 threaded bar + screw nuts + butterfly nuts
- Mini360 DC-DC Buck Converter Step Down Module 
- GSM Module
  . https://www.adafruit.com/product/1946
    https://learn.adafruit.com/fona-tethering-to-raspberry-pi-or-beaglebone-black
  . https://www.aliexpress.com/item/SIM800L-Quad-band-Network-Mini-GPRS-GSM-Breakout-Module/32431547125.html
  . https://www.rhydolabz.com/wiki/?p=16325


